title: SG Wannabe's Kim Jin Ho releases behind-the-scenes of 'Graduation Photo' | allkpop.com
text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me SG Wannabe's Kim Jin Ho releases behind-the-scenes of 'Graduation Photo' By KpopJoA 8 minutes ago 901 0 0 0 Google+ Following the teaser video, SG Wannabe 's Kim Jin Ho unveiled behind-the-scenes footage of "Graduation Photo." 
The singer attended a graduation ceremony taking place in a school on a snowy day in which his song was inspired. Greeted by many students and teachers, Kim Jin Ho performed on stage and conversed with his audience. 
"Graduation Photo" will be released on February 16.
